### Authentication - Login as Candidate
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "amara.jones@example.com",
  "password": "password"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.token);
%}

### Get Candidate Profile
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/candidates/me
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Update Candidate Profile
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/candidates/me/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "summary": "Experienced nurse looking for locum shifts.",
  "primaryDiscipline": "Nursing",
  "band": "Band 5",
  "currentLocation": "London",
  "availabilityStatus": "AVAILABLE",
  "availabilityNotes": "Looking for night shifts mostly."
}

### Add Availability
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/candidates/me/availability
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "availableFrom": "2023-11-01",
  "availabilityType": "AVAILABLE",
  "notes": "Available for night shifts starting November."
}

### Get Compliance Dashboard
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/candidates/me/compliance
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Get Placements
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/candidates/me/placements
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Get Timesheets
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/candidates/me/timesheets
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Authentication - Login as Admin
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin@tophat.com",
  "password": "password"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("admin_token", response.body.token);
%}

### Admin - List Candidates
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/candidates
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Admin - Get Candidate Details
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/candidates/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000201
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Admin - List Jobs
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/jobs
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Admin - Create Job
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/jobs
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clientId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000301",
  "title": "Emergency Nurse",
  "discipline": "Nursing",
  "band": "Band 5",
  "employmentType": "LOCUM",
  "description": "Urgent requirement for A&E.",
  "payRateMin": 25.00,
  "payRateMax": 35.00,
  "status": "PUBLISHED"
}
